edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2014.group19.foodApp.client
Class Post

java.lang.Object
  edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2014.group19.foodApp.client.Post
Direct Known Subclasses:
AcceptancePost, ContactPost, MealPost
public class Post
extends java.lang.Object

The ability to add a custom message or additional information. The ability to add a list of recipients who will receive the post -- Subset of user's contacts. The ability to add a recipient who is currently unavailable. The ability to set notification post time -- The user can choose when the notification is posted (perhaps at a later time or date).
